name: HumanProfile
attributes:
- Age: Numerical (0-120 years, normal distribution)
- Gender: Categorical (options: Male, Female, Non-binary, Other)
- Extraversion: Numerical (1-10 scale, uniform distribution)
- Agreeableness: Numerical (1-10 scale, uniform distribution)
- Conscientiousness: Numerical (1-10 scale, uniform distribution)
- Neuroticism: Numerical (1-10 scale, uniform distribution)
- Openness: Numerical (1-10 scale, uniform distribution)
- Background: Text (brief history)
- Is Employed: Boolean (current employment status)
